Container:
==========
Running instance of docker image is container.

POD:
====
Running instance of deployment manifest is pod.A pod can have more than once container.

Deployment:
===========
A deployment is kubernetes component or manifest for launching a pod.

docker run -d image_name.


Deployment offer
================
1.auto healing
2.auto scaling


               Deployment
                  |
                  |
               Replicaset------------->Controller.
                  |
              p1  p2  p3

Deployment is a kubernetes resource.
Running instance of deployment is pod
Container is running instance of docker image inside pod.



